{"arkId":"cl010112690","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112690","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Cercle d\u0027arpentage","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Cercle d\u0027arpentage"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Philippe d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans (1715-1723) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1720","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 609 - Nicolas et Simone Landau, Vitrine 5","room":"Salle 609, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1720,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"1er quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Langlois, Claude","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Fabricant, facteur","authenticationType":"marque (estampilles, poin\u00e7ons...)","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q48836774"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10691","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"instrument scientifique (mesure, calcul, observation, etc.)","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"\u0022L\u2019instrument est constitu\u00e9 d\u2019un disque en partie \u00e9vid\u00e9 mont\u00e9 sur un pied \u00e0 genou. Il est grav\u00e9 sur sa circonf\u00e9rence d\u2019une \u00e9chelle de 360 degr\u00e9s avec une double num\u00e9rotation en sens inverse (chacune 10-180 X 2) ; les deux diam\u00e8tres, orn\u00e9s de feuillage, portent, au revers, la signature. Quatre pinnules non rabattables, avec une fente et une fen\u00eatre chacune, sont viss\u00e9es sur la circonf\u00e9rence. L\u2019alilade, qui tourne avec la boussole, est munie d\u2019un index qui pointe sur l\u2019\u00e9chelle circulaire ; elle poss\u00e8de deux pinnules du m\u00eame type que les pr\u00e9c\u00e9dentes. La boussole, dont l\u2019aiguille a la forme d\u2019une fl\u00e8che, est inscrite sur son fond d\u2019une rose des vents \u00e0 seize directions avec une fleur de lys au nord, les noms fran\u00e7ais des quatre points cardinaux et les noms abr\u00e9g\u00e9s de quatre collat\u00e9raux ; autour de la rose des vents une \u00e9chelle de quatre fois 90 degr\u00e9s est grav\u00e9e sur une plate-forme (O-90-0 X 2 en partant du nord).\u0022 (Fr\u00e9montier-Murphy, 2002, p. 283)","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; \u0022C- Langlois A Paris\u0022 (au dos, sur l\u0027un des diam\u00e8tres du cercle)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"14","displayDimension":"14 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"16","displayDimension":"16 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Alliage cuivreux, verre, argenture, acier bleui\r\nMat\u00e9riau : alliage cuivreux\r\nMat\u00e9riau : verre\r\nTechnique : argent\u00e9 = argenture (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : acier (bleui)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Nicolas Landau (1887-1979) ; legs Marcelle Landau, 1980","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Landau, Nicolas","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Mme Landau, Marcelle","note":" (don d\u0027un ensemble de 166 instruments scientifiques, en ex\u00e9cution des volont\u00e9s de son \u00e9poux Nicolas Landau)","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don manuel","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1979","startYear":1979,"endYear":1979},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"22\/11\/1979","startYear":1979,"endYear":1979}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don manuel"}],"period":[{"value":"Philippe d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans (1715-1723)"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"}],"objectType":[{"value":"instrument scientifique (mesure, calcul, observation, etc.)"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Fr\u00e9montier-Murphy, Camille, Les Instruments de math\u00e9mathiques, XVIe-XVIIIe si\u00e8cle : cadrans solaires, astrolabes, globes, n\u00e9cessaires de math\u00e9matiques, instruments d\u0027arpentage, microscopes, Paris, R\u00e9union des mus\u00e9es nationaux (RMN), 2002","bibliographyDate":"2002","bibliographyDetail":"p. 283, ill. p. 283, N\u00b0 165","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000112690\/0000953476_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000112690\/0000953476_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2012 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000112690\/0000953478_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000112690\/0000953478_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2012 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/0000000021\/0000112690\/0000953481_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000112690\/0000953481_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2012 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"",